澎湃新闻综合报道14日，一名男子发布微博称，在湖北省全封路的情况下，通过“当官的”父亲的关系派车，自己从天门回到荆州，引发不少网友的质疑。
A man posted a micro-blog on the 14th, saying he had sent cars through his "official" father's relationship to Jingzhou under the complete closure of Hubei Province, prompting a lot of netizens to question.
他还曾发过一段视频称“天门拜拜”。
He also sent a video saying "Good-bye to Tianmen."
自2020年1月24日13时起，天门市已经封闭全市公路进出口通道，含国省道路、县乡道路、村组道路，所有车辆、人员一律禁止通行。
As of 1300 hours on January 24, 2020, the city of Tianmen has closed the city's road access roads, including provincial roads, county and township roads, village roads, all vehicles and personnel are not allowed to pass.
另外，Euamoter在1月6日，通过微博晒出支付宝年度账单，图中显示，2019年全年总支出286万余元。
Also, on January 6, Euamoter posted its annual payout bill through Weibo, which shows a total expenditure of more than $2.86 million for the year 2019.
多个相关话题都上了微博热搜。
A number of related topics on the Weibo hot search.
不少网友评论：你爹要大意失荆州。
Many netizens comment: Your father wants to be disappointed Jingzhou.
麻妹本妹：大意失荆州小飞燕与海：实力派坑爹清尘点点：呵呵，坑爹+1，很好～估计已经被爹暴揍。
Minmei: Big Brother State Flying Swallow and Sea: Powerful Pit Pit Dad Clean Dust: Ha ha, Pit Dad + 1, very good ~ estimated to have been hit by dad.
