15日凌晨，该男子在微博上发布道歉书称，其父亲叫何炎仿，是荆州市商务部门的一名科长，无权派车把他从天门接回。
Early Friday morning, the man issued an apology on Weibo, said his father's name is Yan-imitation, is a section chief of the commercial department of Jingzhou, has no right to send a car to pick him up from the Tianmen Gate.
由于自己急于回家，其父亲利用朋友关系，在天门联系了一辆生活物资的返程车辆将其带回。
In his eagerness to return home, his father took advantage of a friendship and contacted a return vehicle of supplies in Tianmen to bring him back.
“因为虚荣心作怪，在网上宣称是我父亲派车接回的。
"Because of my vanity, I claimed on the Internet that my father had sent for it.
”他也解释了支付宝年度账单截图是其经营的流水账单，并不是父亲给予的。
He also explained that Alipay's annual billing was a running water bill, not from his father.
据中青报·中青网，公开信息显示，何炎仿为荆州市商务局市场运行调节科科长。
According to Zhongqing News Zhongqing net, open information shows, He Yan imitates the section chief of market operation regulation of Jingzhou commercial bureau.
记者多次联系何炎仿，未获得他对此事的回应。
Reporters repeatedly contacted Ho Yan-copy, did not get his response to this matter.
警方：有关部门正在调查核实15日凌晨，@荆州网警巡查执法 发布微博称称当事人何昊已在网上公开致歉，有关部门也正在对此事做进一步调查核实。
Police: the relevant departments are investigating and verifying the early morning, @ Jingzhou cyber police patrol law enforcement issued Weibo said that the concerned Ho has publicly apologized on the Internet, the relevant departments are also further investigation to verify the matter.
